OBO Foundry Metadata

obofoundry_metadata.Rd

Metadata about OBO Foundry ontologies.

Usage

obofoundry_metadata

Format

A data frame with 22 variables:

id
title
domain
description
activity_status
is_obsolete
replaced_by
ontology_purl
preferred_prefix
homepage
contact_name
contact_email
contact_github
license_label
taxon_id
taxon_label
twitter
facebook
publications
in_foundry_order
in_foundry
build_infallible

Source

http://www.obofoundry.org/registry/ontologies.jsonld, last accessed 2021-11-05.
